{
  "stem": "1518.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, when we came to Sumy, we were stationed on top of a mountain, like below the Russian village, and there, they-- they trained us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us uniforms and trained us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have no guns, but they gave us like sticks, brooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we got through it in a couple of months of very hard training there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish Army, the officers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then from Sumy, they send us down to Kiwerce.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kiwerce is near Lutsk, already, in Poland, Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came down to Kiwerce in uniform and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they, like, they separate us to each, you know, the company here, you know, the division, company, battalion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Me, the commander was General Laskin and Colonel Sadovski.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was from [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I came down there in uniform, he took me in with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was with him for about two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had a adjutant with his own jeep, a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His name was Nikoli Kolya.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Again, the other-- the general, he had also his own jeep and a adjutant, and his name was Janek.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were both Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in Kiwerce, they stayed in the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They each had a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was guarded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had-- they had female guard there, there was a whole company of Polish, you know, like girls in the army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they-- they were guarding like you know, gasoline, and-- and ammunition dumps, and the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was with that colonel for about two months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Like, with him, stayed with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I used to go with him to the meetings, like the, you know, the war meetings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have nothing at the time, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I remember what's his name, Rekosovski.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
